name: Qubeee
description:
Qubeee is an action platformer, where you get to control a character named Qubeee.  

Help Qubeee through 40 levels full of deadly traps and various dangers as fast as you can. 

Each level can be replayed to master the game and improve your total time

Game status: 

As for now, Qubeee  has one zone called Factory that contains 40 different levels of various difficulties

The games is planned to be released on Android with more zones, levels, reworked SFX and leaderboards for each zone if it gets enough interest from players 

Follow the game on Twitter for more news and updates
